{"tid":808338,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★傳微軟擬在中國數據中心用華為AI晶片","createTime":"2018-09-06T09:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T10:01:09.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1e938334190a5cd9935ded03c5e1886cef648a25","tid":808338,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T09:06:17.000Z","msg":"科技資訊網站The Information引用消息人士指，微軟正考慮在其中國多個數據中心，使用華為的新開發的人工智能（AI）晶片，雙方目前正進行初步階段商討。<br />\n<br />\n微軟旗下的機器學習程序及人工智能計算功能的數據中心，均使用Nvidia晶片。報道指微軟只打算在中國數據中心使用華為晶片。微軟、華為及NVIDIA的代表均拒絕就報道發表評論。<br />\n<br />\n華為高層近月一直向微軟負責AI及研究的全球執行副總裁沈向洋兜售AI晶片。但因微軟要求相當嚴格，華為工程師正在定制軟件，並用微軟算法，例如使用Bing搜索引擎語音識別軟件來測試晶片，讓晶片達到微軟標準。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/232220/%E7%BE%8E%E6%BE%B3%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA%E5%BE%8C%E8%BD%89%E6%A9%9F-%E5%82%B3%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9F%E6%93%AC%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%94%A8%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BAai%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F232220%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25B0%2581%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25BD%2589%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BB%259F%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%259C%25A8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BAai%25E6%2599%25B6%25E7%2589%2587&d=cDinVvufwTKkQuZWXBaguLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=3ce68a30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/232220/%E7%BE%8E%E6%BE%B3%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA%E5%BE%8C%E8%BD%89%E6%A9%9F-%E5%82%B3%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9F%E6%93%AC%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%94%A8%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BAai%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87</a>"},{"pid":"e0ae49848d96ab3c73cd994a12432d88b4b510be","tid":808338,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T09:06:26.000Z","msg